{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "be43f003-f2ee-44ce-8c82-b036ff5383c7", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/be43f003-f2ee-44ce-8c82-b036ff5383c7@1.pkg/1772597689850/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597691000", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/be43f003-f2ee-44ce-8c82-b036ff5383c7@1.pkg/1772597689850/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597691000"}, "identifier": "be43f003-f2ee-44ce-8c82-b036ff5383c7", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查正确对待挫折的方法、磨砺坚强意志。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③：在风雨洗礼中成长、在历经考验中壮大，体现出要保持乐观心态、培养坚强意志，故③④符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①：积极努力是取得进步成长的重要因素，但不是唯一因素，故①说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②：阳光心态有助于战胜困难，但&ldquo;战胜一切&rdquo;说法夸大，故②说法错误；&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选D。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"margin-left: 0.17in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span>（改编）国家主席习近平在二○二五年新年贺词中指出：&ldquo;我们从来都是在风雨洗礼中成长、在历经考验中壮大，大家要充满信心。&rdquo;这启示我们（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.17in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span>①只要积极努力，就能取得进步和成长</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.17in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span>②充满信心，拥有阳光心态可战胜一切</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.17in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span>③保持乐观向上的心态，培养坚强意志</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④增强生命韧性，培养克服困难的勇气</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）国家主席习近平在二○二五年新年贺词中指出：“我们从来都是在风雨洗礼中成长、在历经考验中壮大，大家要充满信心。”这启示我们（   ）①只要积极努力，就能取得进步和成长②充满信心，拥有阳光心态可战胜一切③保持乐观向上的心态，培养坚强意志④增强生命韧性，培养克服困难的勇气", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/be43f003-f2ee-44ce-8c82-b036ff5383c7@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755250441436", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①②</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①③</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②④</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed":